### Introduction

To fully benefit from ORCID, it is essential that your ORCID registration is publicly visible and connected to the VU Pure research database. This ensures that your current affiliation and previous output are automatically added to your ORCID profile and that in the future new information from your ORCID is automatically added to your VU research profile.
This guide will show you how to register a new ORCID and to connect it to Pure. If you already have an pre-existing ORCID, you can find instructions on how to connect this to your Pure account by [following this link]().

